==English==
===Noun===
'''salvation'''
# (''religion'') the process of being saved, the state of having been saved (from hell)
# The process of being restored or made new for the purpose of becoming saved; the process of being rid of the old poor quality conditions and becoming improved. see ''salvage''
# Reffered to the process taken when Jesus Christ restores all the sinners life when he had washed and made the sinners new through his death on the cross.

